# CLI Package

## Structure

```
packages/cli/src/
  index.ts           # bin entry
  commands/
    scan.ts          # default scan command
    install.ts       # cursor rule install (v0.1.0)
  utils/
    parse-args.ts
```

## Constraints

- Use commander for CLI parsing
- `--json` outputs ONLY JSON to stdout (no colors, no extra text)
- `--fail-below` sets exit code 1 when score below threshold
- Exit codes: 0=pass, 1=fail-below, 2=scan error
- All flags documented in `--help`

## Public Surface

Changing flags/commands requires `product-thinking` skill first.
Update `--help` text in the same PR.
